br />\n要跟你說請忘了我又故作堅強<br />\n「気付いて欲しいよ」って 今更伝えたら<br />\n事到如今才希望你注意到我<br />\nやっぱり 困った顔して笑うかな？<br />\n可能僅換來尷尬的笑容吧<br />\n今の日々を愛さないで<br />\n請別去熱愛現在的日常<br />\nそこには僕はいないんだよ<br />\n在那裡已沒有我的身影<br />\n何気ないことが幸せだったって<br />\n你說細瑣小事都感到幸福<br />\n当たり前でしょう&hellip;<br />\n都是理所當然<br />\nもしも願い叶うのなら<br />\n假如願望真能實現<br />\n隣で笑ってくれるのなら<br />\n希望你能在身旁微笑<br />\n愛を教えてくれた君とまた<br />\n願能與教會我愛的含義的你<br />\nもう一度会いたい<br />\n再一次相遇"},{"pid":"8d05233eac9dfea5143fb4a91c38c671a589ce2b","tid":459023,"uid":88235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:35:17.000Z","msg":"小さな恋のうた<br />\n個人最鐘意倖田來未版<br />\n但我知道大家都鐘意結衣bb 就比你地J下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z8F-Xto_gcY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz8F-Xto_gcY&d=Hvgrx4ZACs2XLgKAvaCYyqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6ddc5524\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z8F-Xto_gcY</a>"},{"pid":"0c0bad48c68e4366d9854f52374915d362c32d21","tid":459023,"uid":110832,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:46:02.000Z","msg":"greeeen - kiseki"},{"pid":"64d47b0a581cee54cd722faaad631ccb510cb7c1","tid":459023,"uid":140222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:46:04.000Z","msg":"spitz - cherry"},{"pid":"9322f2a6dbe799de80b60c5f681f77ae8b766265","tid":459023,"uid":28720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:58:04.000Z","msg":"スピッツ　空も飛べるはず<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda08fb27bbbcdd825cce4f00368d3d7bb9ce884","tid":459023,"uid":36473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:19:57.000Z","msg":"タイナカサチ-tomorrow"},{"pid":"1ef406b97d22bca006ad986be69b99e9b74c740c","tid":459023,"uid":37258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:23:39.000Z","msg":"中島美嘉 - 僕が死のうと思ったのは<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QL3T2Nzcqcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQL3T2Nzcqcs&d=Hvgrx4ZACs2XLgK